Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Head MRI
When I select 'Visual disturbances' from 'Previous interventions/therapies' dropdown menu
Then 'Add clinic' button is enabled
And 'Visual field loss' radio button is enabled
And 'Bitemporal hemianopsia' radio button is enabled
And 'Homonymous hemianopsia' radio button is enabled
And 'Cortical blindness' radio button is enabled
And 'Diplopia' radio button is enabled
And 'Visual acuity loss' radio button is enabled
And 'Blurred vision' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Visual field loss' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Homonymous hemianopsia' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Visual acuity loss' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Blurred vision' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
